<font color="red">
<p><font size="6">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Middleware</font></p>
<p><font size="5">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; A technology that facilitates seamless integration of 
components across platforms and multiple deployments, allowing an enterprise to 
construct solutions by composition of existing software assets irrespective of 
their implementation technology.</font></p>
<p><font size="5">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; It is a &quot;glue&quot;, rather than a design.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<p><p>
Middleware can be used to glue the layers together.
</font></p>
